sequenceDiagram
    actor Vendor as Vendor
    participant Page as TemplateSearchPage <<user interaction>>
    participant Controller as WorkshopTemplateController <<coordinator>>
    participant Service as WorkshopTemplateService <<service>>
    participant WorkshopTemplate as WorkshopTemplate <<entity>>
    participant DB as DB

    Vendor->>Page: 1. Enter filter criteria and search
    activate Page
    Page->>Controller: 2. searchWorkshopTemplates(keyword, name, status, vendorId, tagId, minPrice, maxPrice, minDuration, maxDuration, minRating)
    activate Controller
    Controller->>Service: 3. searchWorkshopTemplates(filterParams)
    activate Service

    Service->>Service: 4. Build combined Specification from non-null filter params
    Service->>WorkshopTemplate: 5. findAll(specification)
    activate WorkshopTemplate
    WorkshopTemplate->>DB: 6. SELECT workshop_template with dynamic criteria (JPA Criteria API)
    activate DB
    DB-->>WorkshopTemplate: Matching template records
    deactivate DB
    WorkshopTemplate-->>Service: List~WorkshopTemplate~
    deactivate WorkshopTemplate

    alt 6A. No templates match filters
        Service-->>Controller: 6A1. Empty List~WorkshopTemplateResponse~
        Controller-->>Page: 6A2. 200 OK + ApiResponse~[]~
        Page-->>Vendor: 6A3. Show empty state: "No templates found"
    else 6B. Templates found
        Service->>Service: 7. Map each template via mapToResponse()
        Service-->>Controller: 8. List~WorkshopTemplateResponse~
        deactivate Service
        Controller-->>Page: 9. 200 OK + ApiResponse~List~WorkshopTemplateResponse~~
        deactivate Controller
        Page-->>Vendor: 10. Display filtered template results
        deactivate Page
    end
